    org.apache.drill.exec.ExecConstants.ENABLE_BULK_LOAD_TABLE_LIST_KEY
    option. It will not take any effect. The option added as part of DRILL-4577, was used to mark that hive tables should be loaded for all table names at once. Then as part of DRILL-4826 was added option to regulate bulk size, because big amount of views was causing performance degradation. After last improvements for DRILL-7115 both options (ExecConstants.ENABLE_BULK_LOAD_TABLE_LIST_KEY and ExecConstants.BULK_LOAD_TABLE_LIST_BULK_SIZE_KEY) became obsolete and may be removed in future releases.
